<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">

<Paragraph FontFamily="Segoe UI" FontSize="12pt">
This sample illustrates document editor using SfRichTextBoxAdv control that is similar to Microsoft Word with Ribbon options.
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph FontFamily="Segoe UI" FontSize="12pt">
The following screenshot displays the same.
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph TextAlignment ="Center"><Image Source="Images\DocumentEditor.png" Stretch="None" /></Paragraph>   


<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}" FontFamily="Segoe UI" FontSize="12pt">Features</TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>

<List FontFamily="Segoe UI" FontSize="12pt">
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports to view, print and edit Word, RTF, HTML, XAML and text documents.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports undo and redo editing operations.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports cut, copy, and paste the rich-text to and from the SfRichTextBoxAdv.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports drag and drop the rich-text to and from the SfRichTextBoxAdv.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports to find and replace text in a document.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Add notes to the document using Word-like comment support.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports right to left text, paragraph, list and table.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports three view types: page by page, continuous (single-page view), and block.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Support for restricting user editing and encrypting the word document with password.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports context menu, mini toolbar and shortcut keys for all necessary editing operations.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports commands that can be used for XAML command binding with UI elements.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

</FlowDocument>